ata is processed and tokenised by Stripe — KVRN never stores raw card numbers. When you join our waitlist, we collect your email address and, if you opt in, your phone number. We also collect standard web analytics data (pages viewed, referral source, device type) via Google Analytics.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"How we use it\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"02\",\". \",\"How we use it\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Order data is used to process and fulfil your purchase, communicate about your order, and handle returns. Waitlist data is used solely to notify you of new collection releases. Analytics data is used to understand how people use the site so we can improve it. We do not sell your data to third parties. We do not use your data for advertising.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Who we share it with\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"03\",\". \",\"Who we share it with\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Your data is shared with the services necessary to operate the business: Stripe (payments), Shippo (shipping labels), Resend (email), Twilio (SMS, if opted in), Neon (database), and Google Analytics. All providers are bound by data processing agreements. We do not share your data with any other parties.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Cookies\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"04\",\". \",\"Cookies\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"We use essential cookies required for the site to function (cart state, session management) and analytics cookies (Google Analytics, Microsoft Clarity). Analytics cookies are only set after you give consent via our cookie notice. You can withdraw consent at any time via our Cookie Policy page.\"}]]}],\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\"]}],\"$L1b\"]}]}],null,\"$L1c\"]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L1d\",null,{\"children\":\"$L1e\"}],null],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$20\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L21\"}]}]}]]}]\n22:I[4431,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n24:I[5278,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\n18:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Your rights\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"05\",\". \",\"Your rights\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"You have the right to access the personal data we hold about you, request correction of inaccurate data, request deletion of your data, and withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time. To exercise any of these rights, email hello@kvrn.com.\"}]]}]\n19:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Retention\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"06\",\". \",\"Retention\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Order data is retained for 7 years to comply with tax and accounting obligations. Marketing consent records are retained until you withdraw consent. Analytics data is retained for 14 months in Google Analytics.\"}]]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Contact\",{\"className\":\"py-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-6 md:gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light\",\"children\":[\"07\",\". \",\"Contact\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"For any privacy-related questions, email hello@kvrn.com. We aim to respond within 5 business days.\"}]]}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":[\"Questions?\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\",\"className\":\"text-[var(--color-text)] underline underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\",\"children\":\"hello@kvrn.com\"}]]}]}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"$L22\",null,{\"children\":[\"$L23\",[\"$\",\"$L24\",null,{\"promise\":\"$@25\"}]]}]\n1e:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"theme-color\",\"content\":\"#FAFAF8\"}]]\n23:null\n26:I[622,[],\"IconMark\"]\n25:{\"metadata\":[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Privacy Policy — KVRN | KVRN\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"KVRN heavyweight fleece. 400 GSM+ oversized hoodies and sweatpants. Double-layered hood. Concealed interior zippers. No drawstrings. Quiet luxury.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"author\",\"content\":\"KVRN\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"manifest\",\"href\":\"/site.webmanifest\",\"crossOrigin\":\"$undefined\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"name\":\"keywords\",\"content\":\"heavyweight hoodie,400 gsm